{"ts":"2026-05-05T20:23:13.078Z","author":"codex-maintainer","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/comments/10","value":{"created_at":"2026-05-05T20:23:13.078Z","author":"codex-maintainer","text":"External gate hardening evidence: focused release workflow regressions passed (39 tests), unauthenticated telemetry-mode off Sentry gate returns checked=false with missing_sentry_auth_token warning, local token-backed Sentry gate reports zero fatal/error issues, and node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json passed all checks with 1211 tests at 100 percent coverage."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/front_matter/updated_at","value":"2026-05-05T20:23:13.078Z"}],"before_hash":"15507b78a8aa2ba0b534a740718de1b8a39ca198f45931f3c20b9d61eb278339","after_hash":"f9a508b1190b0ac741f3a2273cf29736c952b1f1ec293a0c66bf27262b6475d9"}
{"ts":"2026-05-05T20:45:40.935Z","author":"codex-maintainer","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/comments/11","value":{"created_at":"2026-05-05T20:45:40.935Z","author":"codex-maintainer","text":"Auto Release run 25400874495 succeeded and pushed release commit 0f04597/tag v2026.5.5, but GitHub did not start the tag-triggered Release workflow because GITHUB_TOKEN push events do not create normal workflow runs. Adding workflow_dispatch-by-tag support to Release and making Auto Release dispatch and wait for that publish workflow after a new tag is pushed."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/front_matter/updated_at","value":"2026-05-05T20:45:40.935Z"}],"before_hash":"f9a508b1190b0ac741f3a2273cf29736c952b1f1ec293a0c66bf27262b6475d9","after_hash":"a0dbc34ae0222aac80f79466e6d5c27c49afdb38478d4030ba403ad8e37b2afd"}
{"ts":"2026-05-05T20:53:03.777Z","author":"codex-maintainer","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/comments/12","value":{"created_at":"2026-05-05T20:53:03.777Z","author":"codex-maintainer","text":"Release dispatch automation evidence: YAML parsing passed for auto-release/release workflows, focused workflow contract tests passed (9 tests), full node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json passed on version 2026.5.5 with 1211 tests at 100 percent coverage, and tracked secret scan plus diff token scan found no private token/IP leakage."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/front_matter/updated_at","value":"2026-05-05T20:53:03.777Z"}],"before_hash":"a0dbc34ae0222aac80f79466e6d5c27c49afdb38478d4030ba403ad8e37b2afd","after_hash":"28c6dc42aec45792a85d98f226364287b26b409334b5b8196bfbd07f6b4e1700"}
{"ts":"2026-05-05T21:01:02.871Z","author":"codex-maintainer","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/comments/13","value":{"created_at":"2026-05-05T21:01:02.871Z","author":"codex-maintainer","text":"Release retry 25401715352 failed before npm publish at Sentry issue threshold: GitHub SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN is present but lacks issue-read scope and returned sentry_api_403. Adjusting release workflow so GitHub-hosted issue threshold requires SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN, while SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN remains for release/sourcemap upload. Focused workflow contracts, YAML parse, and tracked secret scan pass."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/front_matter/updated_at","value":"2026-05-05T21:01:02.871Z"}],"before_hash":"28c6dc42aec45792a85d98f226364287b26b409334b5b8196bfbd07f6b4e1700","after_hash":"77dea64ce22198abe3fb84889d8bddc142eda1de2d5fb568606f58681635b115"}
{"ts":"2026-05-05T21:10:19.818Z","author":"codex-maintainer","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/comments/14","value":{"created_at":"2026-05-05T21:10:19.818Z","author":"codex-maintainer","text":"Release retry 25402097202 successfully published npm package 2026.5.5 with provenance and passed npm/npx/bunx verification, then failed only at GitHub Release creation because workflow_dispatch runs need explicit tag_name. Updated release workflow to pass tag_name and skip duplicate npm publish when the target version already exists, making retry safe. Focused workflow contracts, YAML parse, and tracked secret scan pass."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/front_matter/updated_at","value":"2026-05-05T21:10:19.818Z"}],"before_hash":"77dea64ce22198abe3fb84889d8bddc142eda1de2d5fb568606f58681635b115","after_hash":"51274c763891c4542b3e4b8aca9ad712aaac7adf989c033c54a8a7c13c168925"}
